The Apostle Paul gives us some more indications on what your student can enjoy.

00:07:55.699 --> 00:08:02.699
Please, notice with me what he says at Colossians chapter 2 and verse 7.

00:08:02.699 --> 00:08:08.699
He said in verse 6 that they should keep on walking but then in verse 7 that they should be rooted

00:08:08.699 --> 00:08:13.699
and built up in him, Jesus, and being stabilized into faith.

00:08:13.699 --> 00:08:18.699
Just as you were taught and then overflowing with thanksgiving.

00:08:18.699 --> 00:08:24.699
So their appreciation, their gratitude, they will want to go to the meetings and worship Jehovah.

00:08:24.699 --> 00:08:33.700
So continue to find joy in helping your student feed themselves spiritually but also help them to appreciate attending meetings on a weekly basis.

00:08:33.700 --> 00:08:39.700
Make it a way of life for them so they can enjoy everlasting life.

